Package: similR
Type: Package
Title: Local Recommendation of Institutional Scientific Literature
Version: 0.4.0.9004
Authors@R:
    person(
      given = "Henry",
      family = "Osorto",
      email = "henry.osorto@unitec.edu.hn",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides a local Shiny application and reproducible data pipeline
    for recommending institutional scientific literature. The package imports,
    cleans, deduplicates, versions, validates, and stores bibliographic records
    in DuckDB databases distributed through GitHub Releases. The lexical
    recommendation engine combines TF-IDF, BM25, exact-term matching, and
    dimension-specific weights. An optional local semantic engine integrates
    multilingual Sentence Transformer embeddings through reticulate while
    preserving a fully functional lexical fallback when Python is unavailable.
